article.headline: Price propels Marist to 77-62 victory over Rider
article.description: — Jackson Price scored 17 points and Marist beat Rider 77-62 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Price propels Marist to 77-62 victory over Rider
article.story: LAWRENCEVILLE, N.J. -- — Jackson Price scored 17 points and Marist beat Rider 77-62 on Saturday night. Price was 5 of 10 shooting, including 1 for 4 from 3-point range, and went 6 for 7 from the line for the Red Foxes (13-9, 8-5 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Max Allen had 16 points, while Jadin Collins scored 11. Tariq Ingraham finished with 14 points to pace the Broncs (8-16, 5-8). TJ Weeks Jr. added 13 points and Allen Powell scored 12. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
